data.description: GREAT OPPORTUNITY! You can make this your dream home at just 5.25% interest. Welcome to Winter Haven, home to beautiful lakes and LEGOLAND. This 2022 beautiful property offers 4 bedrooms, 2 baths and plenty of floor space with 1,850 sqft. Contemporary kitchen cabinet design with stainless steel appliances and a spacious island to gather around with the family. New roof, a/c unit and water heater (all 2022). Beautiful high quality vinyl flooring and other features are waiting for you. You will fall in love with the neighborhood and the surrounding areas. Welcome to your new home!
